OL,4,G0350FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe first visit is to the Oxenham
OL,6,     GArms in Devon, where Simon and
OL,7,     GLyn help their guests brush up on
OL,8,     Gthe local pastime of broom
OL,9,     Gdancing. But one guest's feedback
OL,10,     Ghas the hosts vowing revenge.
OL,11,G0420FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GJohn Brady likes to stand out
OL,13,     Gfrom the crowd in Liverpool with
OL,14,     Ghis unique B&B, Elegant House.
OL,15,     GBut his eclectic style and
OL,16,     Galternative breakfast aren't to
OL,17,     Geveryone's taste.
