OL,4,G0445FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GPeter and Amanda introduce their
OL,6,     Gguests to the world of glamping
OL,7,     Gat Hidden Valley Yurts in
OL,8,     GMonmouthshire. But the shared
OL,9,     Gbathroom facilities and DIY
OL,10,     Gbreakfast aren't to everyone's
OL,11,     Gtaste.
OL,12,G0515FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GDavid and Nikki host the final
OL,14,     Gvisit at Cley Hall Hotel in
OL,15,     GSpalding, Lincolnshire. But
OL,16,     Gthere's clock-watching at
OL,17,     Gbreakfast, and some of the
OL,18,     Gguests' comments leave the hosts
OL,19,     Gfuming.
